## Why This File Exists

This PATENTS file provides explicit patent peace to users and contributors of
Sur5 Lite. Many open source licenses (like MIT) do not include explicit patent
grants, which can create uncertainty for commercial users.

Key benefits of this grant:
1. **Clarity:** Explicit permission to use any Sur5ve LLC patents in the Software
2. **Protection:** Defensive termination discourages patent trolling
3. **Peace of Mind:** Commercial users can adopt Sur5 Lite with confidence

This approach is modeled after similar patent grants used by major open source
projects (e.g., React, Go, Apache projects).

